{"tid":746694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係香港成立 列寧主義共產黨 ，要廢除私有制，玩唔玩得過？","createTime":"2018-07-17T18:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T13:12:22.000Z","uid":147803,"like":48,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"61713ace81ea4942bbe381a269bf0a4cec954aa7","tid":746694,"uid":147803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T18:08:15.000Z","msg":"主張世界革命消滅地球上所有國家 , 以及廢除私有製<br />\n肯定違反基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n印《共產黨宣言》，周街派，係咪犯法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<em>　　共产党人不屑于隐瞒自己的观点和意图。他们公开宣布：他们的目的只有用暴力推翻全部现存的社会制度才能达到。让统治阶级在共产主义革命面前发抖吧。无产者在这个革命中失去的只是锁链。他们获得的将是整个世界。<br />\n</em><br />\n<br />\n認真，有無人想咁樣一齊玩嘢？"},{"pid":"a956e9a00ddf8cdb0a65fb75c85099b84d610329","tid":746694,"uid":42243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T18:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b781aa49375cfc4f76972dcaa10e0fb89e1ea393","tid":746694,"uid":189053,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T18:12:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71222bb4fb9c6a94888f0adca86606f383f76e56","tid":746694,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T18:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99131d6b11abdab5859d453bc9d96795cb9910c5","tid":746694,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T18:14:39.000Z","msg":"我冇記錯有法例寫明香港唔會成立共產黨"},{"pid":"b518f6ebc2ad23f5ccceb940d66ca9e68fffc84d","tid":746694,"uid":498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T18:15:37.000Z","msg":"好了， 基本法話香港keep住50年不變<br />\n但共朝太監話基本法係附屬係支国憲法下<br />\n但支国係行共產主義， 咁明顯係支憲大過基本法"},{"pid":"9ce136d8268794e30fb664b6b7799c578a6641b5","tid":746694,"uid":157494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"rep